events.name: WWDC 2016 Keynote Live Streaming
events.description:
Some of us are watching the WWDC keynote together at HackerSpaceSG. The event starts at on Monday mid-night at 1AM Singapore Time. Come early to grab a drink and talk to eachother.  
About the event. - https://developer.apple.com/wwdc 
We will get some drinks and food and watch Tim Cook talking about the latest innvotations of Apple.
